# OpenCodeRunner
An open-source code runner that can run project-level (multi-file) codes, including `Python` `Javascript/Typescript` `C/C++` `Java` `Dafny` etc.

## TODO
- [ ] Sandbox 

## Supported Languages
- [x] Python
- [ ] JavaScript
- [ ] TypeScript
- [ ] C
- [ ] C++
- [ ] Java
- [ ] Dafny


## Update

### 2025-04-11
